  <EnumDefinition Description="Country code enumeration list. As referenced in the GIS-331 Wifi Calibration Spec., Contry code will be based on RPO Calibration. As referenced in the GIS-331 Wifi Requirements Specification, this country code calibration is also being used for determining the regulatory wifi power variation settings to use for the wifi chip that shall be dynamically determined and set based on the value (country value) set for this calibration. Note, the value (country value) set for this calibration is determined by the country RPO (Regular Production Options Content) code for a given vehicle based on the PPC (Program Planning Content) for that vehicle, which represents the intended country of sell for that vehicle." Name="COUNTRY_CODE">
    <EnumID>_NiUcILEYEeO_VpIpRoy4MQ</EnumID>
